神级别的人物哈，刚毕业的小白还是好好学习，后期才能去筑梦。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-e72787c98b163fb88a1700ae68200e02_720w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "36 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/493704857"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ilr/o9Nqa39paEAMaCDcxOTkzNDQ2IKurxIsGMAA40gFAL3IJNDkzNzA0ODU3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "48_1639984081.8821425", "card_id": "Q_506556431", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 763}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "相亲多次没有成功，因为颜控，年龄大了，想妥协，但是看到人还是接受不了，应该怎么办？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-51c2592556087ff9b26818cc1f598e1b_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "36 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/506556431"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ilr/o9Nqa39paEAMaCDc0ODQ5NzkzINyr7Y0GMGI4xg9AMHIJNTA2NTU2NDMxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "49_1639984081.882511", "card_id": "Q_505126564", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 48}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "2021 年你和他 / 她拍的第一张照片是哪张？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "2021 年即将过去，这一年中，相信你和爱人、朋友都拍了不少饱含回忆的照片。 现在，我们希望邀请你翻开相册，找到和他 / 她 / 他们拍的第一张照片，一起分享照片背后的故事~ 这里是由 @知乎日报 @知乎数码联合 @知乎小红星共同发起的「平凡人摄影大赛｜2021 镜头里的故事」活动中的一个提问。 比赛详细规则知乎科技：「平凡人摄影大赛 ｜2021 镜头里的故事」正式开启"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-5656ee62a54452349f696830ef54d8e0_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "34 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/505126564"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Ilr/o9Nqa39paEAMaCDc0NTMxNDUwIMDBzI0GMAA4bkAxcgk1MDUxMjY1NjR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}], "paging": {"is_end": true, "next": "", "previous": ""}, "fresh_text": "热榜已更新"}